        <h2>Purpose of Data Use</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>To process and fulfill orders.</li>
            <li>To send promotional emails and gardening tips.</li>
            <li>To improve website experience.</li>
            <li>To comply with legal requirements.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
        <p>We may share data with third parties such as shipping companies, payment processors, and marketing partners, but we do not sell your data without consent.</p>
        
        <h2>Cookies and Tracking</h2>
        <p>We use cookies for website functionality, analytics, and advertising. You can manage cookie preferences through your browser settings.</p>
        
