        <p>Our website may contain links to external sites. Clicking on those means their privacy policies apply, not ours.</p>
        
        <h2>Changes to Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this policy anytime. Continued use of our site implies acceptance of changes.</p>
        
        <h2>Returns & Refund Policy for Plants</h2>
        <div class="important-notice">
            <p><strong>Important:</strong> Plants are living products and are not eligible for return or exchange once purchased and delivered.</p>
        </div>
        <ul>
            <li>Plants are sensitive to changes in environment, handling, and care after leaving our facility.</li>
            <li>We ensure all plants are healthy and well-cared for before shipping.</li>
            <li>Responsibility for plant care passes to the customer upon delivery.</li>
            <li>Plants are perishable and their condition can change quickly.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Exceptions</h2>
        <p>If your plant arrives damaged or unhealthy, please contact us within 24 hours of delivery with photos. We will review your case and may offer a replacement or refund at our discretion.</p>
        
        <p>For any questions about plant care or our policies, please contact us at <a href="mailto:Potbazar014@gmail.com">Potbazar014@gmail.com</a> or WhatsApp: +91 9760653073 (10AM to 6PM, Monday to Saturday).</p>
        
        <a href="/" class="back-to-home">‚Üê Back to Home</a>
    </div>

    <a href="#" class="back-to-top" id="backToTop">‚Üë</a>

    <script>
        // Back to top button functionality
        const backToTop = document.getElementById('backToTop');
        
        window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
            if (window.scrollY > 300) {
                backToTop.classList.add('show');
            } else {
                backToTop.classList.remove('show');
            }
        });

        backToTop.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
            e.preventDefault();
            window.scrollTo({ top: 0, behavior: 'smooth' });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
